TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT TEST_ROSTER.customer_id, TEST_ADMIN.product_id, TEST_ROSTER.student_id, TEST_CATALOG.test_catalog_id, TEST_CATALOG.item_set_id, COUNT (TEST_ADMIN.test_admin_id)
FROM TEST_ROSTER, TEST_ADMIN, TEST_CATALOG, stg_param_winscr_tb
WHERE TEST_ROSTER.test_admin_id = TEST_ADMIN.test_admin_id
AND TEST_ADMIN.test_catalog_id = TEST_CATALOG.test_catalog_id AND TEST_ROSTER.customer_id = TEST_ADMIN.customer_id AND TEST_ADMIN.product_id = TEST_CATALOG.product_id AND TEST_ROSTER.customer_id = stg_param_winscr_tb.customer_id AND TEST_ADMIN.product_id = stg_param_winscr_tb.product_id AND TEST_ROSTER.activation_status = 'AC' AND TEST_ROSTER.test_completion_status NOT IN ('NT', 'SC')
AND ( EXISTS (SELECT NULL FROM ITEM_RESPONSE ir WHERE ir.test_roster_id = TEST_ROSTER.test_roster_id) OR EXISTS (SELECT NULL FROM ITEM_RESPONSE_CR irc WHERE irc.test_roster_id = TEST_ROSTER.test_roster_id) )
GROUP BY TEST_ROSTER.customer_id, TEST_ROSTER.student_id, TEST_ADMIN.product_id, TEST_CATALOG.test_catalog_id, TEST_CATALOG.item_set_id
HAVING COUNT (TEST_ADMIN.test_admin_id) > 1

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: o_h_ERROR_LONG_DESCRIPTION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT stg.customer_id AS customer_id, stg.product_id AS product_id, str.opunit AS opunit, gd.district_org_id as district_org_id, tr.org_node_id AS class_org_id, tr.student_id AS student_id, tr.test_roster_id, tc.item_set_id AS tc_item_set_id, p.product_name AS test_name, tr.form_assignment, tc.eiss_test_level AS test_level, s.barcode AS barcode, tc.commodity_code AS commodity_code, tr.udf AS udf, tr.test_completion_status AS test_completion_status, tr.activation_status AS activation_status, sd.grade gh_grade, s.grade grade, tr.litho_code litho_code
FROM TEST_CATALOG tc, STUDENT s, TEST_ADMIN ta, TEST_ROSTER tr, PRODUCT p, stg_param_winscr_tb stg, STUDENT_ITEM_SET_STATUS si, ITEM_SET it, ORG_NODE_STUDENT ons, student_details sd, stg_test_roster str, group_details gd
WHERE tr.test_admin_id = ta.test_admin_id AND ta.test_catalog_id = tc.test_catalog_id AND tr.customer_id = stg.customer_id AND ta.product_id = stg.product_id AND p.product_id = stg.product_id AND tc.product_id = stg.product_id AND str.opunit = sd.opunit AND s.student_id = tr.student_id AND si.test_roster_id = tr.test_roster_id AND it.item_set_id = si.item_set_id AND it.SAMPLE = 'F' AND tr.student_id = ons.student_id AND tr.org_node_id = ons.org_node_id AND sd.student_id = s.student_id
AND sd.class_org_id = tr.org_node_id AND gd.class_org_id = tr.org_node_id AND tr.test_roster_id = str.test_roster_id

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Check validity of Customer_Id by using an unconnected lookup on CUSTOMER table.

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_EISS_ORG_ERROR

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Check validity of Product_Id by using an unconnected lookup on PRODUCT table.

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Check if district data is present in ORG_NODE_CATEGORY using an unconnected lookup.

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Check if school data is present in ORG_NODE_CATEGORY using an unconnected lookup.

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_SCH_ERROR

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Calling lookup UDF_MAPPING to get value for OAS_COLUMN_NAME.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT
se.DISTRICT_ORG_ID as DISTRICT_ORG_ID,
MAX (c.eiss_org || LPAD (p.eiss_testing_program, 3, 0)) as ORG_TP, MAX (e.struc_lvl) as STRUC_LVL, MAX (e.struc_elm) as STRUCT_ELEMENT,
se.opunit as OPUNIT, MAX (e.elm_name) org_node_name, e.calibration as calibration, e.public_org as public_org, p.eiss_testing_program as testing_prog, sum(to_number(case_count)) as CASE_COUNT
FROM group_details se,
org_node n, product p, customer c, EISS_ORG_BC_TPE e, stg_param_winscr_tb stg, stg_export_parms ep
WHERE
n.org_node_id = se.DISTRICT_ORG_ID
AND p.product_id = stg.product_id AND c.customer_id = stg.customer_id AND n.org_node_code = e.spcl_cd(+) AND c.customer_id = e.customer_id AND p.product_id = e.product_id AND ep.customer_id = e.customer_id AND ep.parameter = 'OPUNIT_LEVEL' AND e.struc_lvl = ep.value
GROUP BY se.opunit,se.DISTRICT_ORG_ID,e.calibration,e.public_org,p.eiss_testing_program

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select jb.district_org_id as district_org_id, jb.org_tp as org_tp , jb.struct_element as struct_element, jb.opunit as opunit, jb.case_count as case_count , jb.date_time as date_time , jb.org_tp_name as org_tp_name , jb.processing_mode as processing_mode, jb.response_provider_name as response_provider_name, gd.class_org_id as class_org_id , gd.district_org_id as district_org_id1 , gd.group_id as group_id, gd.group_grade as group_grade, gd.case_count as case_count1, gd.district_number as district_number, gd.district_name as district_name, gd.school_number as school_number, gd.school_name as school_name , gd.teacher_name as teacher_name , gd.record_status_flag as record_status_flag, gd.opunit as opunit1, sd.student_id as student_id, sd.class_org_id as class_org_id, sd.vendor_student_id as vendor_student_id, sd.last_name as last_name , sd.first_name as first_name , sd.middle_name as middle_name, sd.birth_date as birth_date, sd.gender as gender , sd.grade as grade , sd.customer_student_id as customer_student_id , sd.barcode_id as barcode_id , sd.record_status_flag as record_status_flag1, sd.opunit as opunit2, std.student_test_details_id as student_test_details_id , std.student_id as student_id1, std.grade as grade1 , std.commodity_code as commodity_code , std.litho_code as litho_code , std.test_level as test_level , std.form as form , std.test_name as test_name, std.udf as udf, std.student_special_code as student_special_code , std.test_date_time as test_date_time, std.record_status_flag as record_status_flag2, std.opunit as opunit3 , itd.student_test_details_id as student_test_details_id1, itd.item_id as item_id, itd.item_id_source as item_id_source, itd.ignore_response as ignore_response, itd.last_updated_date_time as last_updated_date_time, itd.item_response as item_response, itd.record_status_flag as record_status_flag3
from group_details gd, job_details jb, student_details sd, student_test_details std,item_details itd
where gd.district_org_id = jb.district_org_id and gd.opunit = jb.opunit and sd.class_org_id = gd.class_org_id and sd.opunit = gd.opunit and sd.grade = gd.group_grade and std.student_id = sd.student_id and sd.opunit = std.opunit and itd.student_test_details_id = substr(std.student_test_details_id,4)
order by jb.district_org_id,jb.opunit,gd.group_id,gd.class_org_id,gd.opunit, sd.student_id,sd.opunit,sd.gender,std.student_test_details_id,std.opunit, itd.student_test_details_id
